# Scenario 1: Add a New Book to Collection
# User Story: As a book enthusiast, I want to add a new book to my collection

### 1. Add "The Hobbit" by J.R.R. Tolkien
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Hobbit",
  "genre": "fantasy", 
  "isbn": "9780547928227",
  "publication_date": "1937-09-21",
  "description": "A reluctant Hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out to the Lonely Mountain with a spirited group of dwarves to reclaim their mountain home - and the gold within it - from the dragon Smaug.",
  "author": {
    "name": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
    "biography": "John Ronald Reuel Tolkien was an English writer, poet, philologist, and academic, best known as the author of the high fantasy works The Hobbit and The Lord of the Rings."
  },
  "reading_status": "want_to_read"
}

